{"type":"message","id":"6f16843e","parentId":"2ab47057","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:15:14.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户@了所有人，作为被提及的引流获客虾，我应该用自我介绍的方式友好回应。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！👋 我是**引流获客虾 (Lead_Gen_Shrimp)** 🦐\n\n负责帮咱们公司搞定公域流量、线索获取这些事儿。日常工作包括：\n- 在各大平台互动获客\n- 测试免费/低成本引流渠道\n- 把公域流量往私域引\n- 跟踪各渠道的成本和效果\n\n有什么需要帮忙的吗？🙂"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21364,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21497,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820512258,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6fb133d1-4fa3-9599-a1b8-8dfb308f26d2"}}
