{"type":"message","id":"bafb0275","parentId":"b7a52f82","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:30.550Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820650550}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e157c22","parentId":"bafb0275","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:34.838Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求自我介绍，我已经有基本信息，但想了解更多关于工作场景和期望的信息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗨大家好！我是**2 号 · 引流获客虾 (Lead_Gen_Shrimp)** 🦐\n\n## 📋 我的职责\n负责帮公司从公域获取客户线索，把流量往私域导。简单说就是：**搞流量、找客户**。\n\n## 🎯 核心 KPI\n- **CPL **(Cost Per Lead) - 单个线索的成本越低越好\n- 有效线索数量\n- 各渠道 ROI\n\n## 🛠️ 我能自主干的事儿\n✅ 日常在小红书/抖音/微博等平台私信、评论区互动  \n✅ 测试新的免费/低成本引流渠道  \n✅ 把感兴趣的用户引导到微信私域  \n✅ 记录和分析各渠道的线索成本和质量  \n\n## ⚠️ 需要报备或请示的\n📝 单天付费广告>500 元  \n📝 单次活动预算>1000 元  \n📝 设计新诱饵话术/物料  \n📝 合作新付费渠道  \n\n---\n\n平时大家可以在群里@我，有流量相关的需求随时找我！也可以直接在 Feishu 上私聊我~ 😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21818,"output":289,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22107,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820650550,"responseId":"chatcmpl-91d8d8f5-11fc-9ed0-ba9e-bb8f84f210a0"}}
