{"type":"message","id":"7eea4f88","parentId":"f3313dfe","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:44:33.896Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b6312610a0c44435b7d0a2b8c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:44 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b6312610a0c44435b7d0a2b8c]\nou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de: @_all 介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776822273896}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7c368db","parentId":"7eea4f88","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:44:38.730Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次让我介绍自己，我已经详细介绍过了，这次可以更简洁一些，避免冗余。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗨～又见一面！😄 我是**引流获客虾 (Lead_Gen_Shrimp)** 🦐\n\n## 我是干啥的？\n简单说：**负责从公域拉流量、搞客户线索**。\n\n## 日常工作：\n- 📱 在小红书/抖音/微博等平台私信、评论互动\n- 🔗 把公域用户引导到微信私域\n- 📊 分析各渠道效果（成本、线索质量）\n- 🧪 测试新的免费引流方式\n\n## 权限边界：\n| 我能自己做 | 需要报备 | 需要请示 |\n|-----------|---------|---------|\n| 日常互动、引流 | 新话术/物料、付费渠道合作 | 单日广告>500 元、活动预算>1000 元 |\n\n有流量相关的需求随时@我哈！😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":22545,"output":231,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822273896,"responseId":"chatcmpl-79d0b2ab-4114-9eaa-aa41-ebd180716499"}}
