{"type":"message","id":"a1071120","parentId":"8bce1c7d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:32.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"笔记已创建并保存到 MEMORY.md，现在需要向用户总结确认学习完成。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存！\n\n## 🌐 Agent Browser (ClawDBot) - 核心要点\n\n**是什么**: 无头浏览器自动化工具，专为 AI 代理优化\n\n**核心特点**:\n- ✅ **Accessibility Tree** 快照 + **Ref-based selection** (`@e1`, `@e2`...)\n- ✅ **Session 隔离** (可以同时运行多个浏览器实例)\n- ✅ **State Persistence** (保存登录态，跳过重复登录)\n\n**核心命令**:\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>              # 打开网页\nagent-browser snapshot -i --json      # 关键：获取 refs\nagent-browser click @e2               # 基于 ref 点击\nagent-browser fill @e3 \"text\"         # 填充输入框\nagent-browser wait --load networkidle # 等待页面加载\n```\n\n**最佳实践**:\n1. 总是用 `-i --json` 参数\n2. 复杂操作前 `wait --load networkidle`\n3. 有登录需求用 `state save/load`\n4. 并行测试用 `--session`\n\n详细学习笔记保存在 `memory/browser-clawdbot-learning.md` 📝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33519,"output":295,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836788761,"responseId":"chatcmpl-778783c3-95ce-9fb1-8925-df182dec314b"}}
