{"type":"message","id":"bbaa6f9c","parentId":"93015669","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:27.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已读完技能文档并保存了学习记录到 memory 文件，现在需要将摘要更新到 MEMORY.md 中，完成用户要求的保存到记忆任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存到记忆！\n\n## 🔍 Skill Finder (中文) - 核心要点\n\n**是什么**: ClawHub Skills 查找器，帮助用户发现需要的技能工具\n\n**触发词**: \"找 skill\"、\"find skill\"、\"搜索 skill\"\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ 核心命令\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"<关键词>\"      # 搜索 skills\nclawhub inspect <name>         # 查看详情\nclawhub install <name>         # 安装\nclawhub list                   # 查看已安装\n```\n\n### ✅ 关键步骤：安装后验证（必须执行！）\n\n```bash\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n```\n\n- **文件存在** = 安装成功 ✅  \n- **文件不存在** = 安装失败 ❌\n\n### 📋 工作流程\n1. 理解需求\n2. 提取关键词\n3. 搜索 → `clawhub search`\n4. 推荐（显示下载量/stars）\n5. 安装 → `clawhub install`\n6. **验证成功** ← 最重要！\n\n### 💡 输出格式\n每个结果应包含：\n- 名称 + 中文描述\n- 下载量 | Stars 数\n- ✅/❌ 是否已安装\n\n详细学习笔记保存在 `memory/skill-finder-cn-learning.md` 📝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":43767,"output":369,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44136,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840384197,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4a9186bd-0fe6-9b46-a722-154c9e8c4b8c"}}
